29 persons and transactions to which that tax applies.
30 (c) The county commission shall provide for the
31 collection and administration of this tax by resolution.
32 (d) The proceeds of this tax shall be deposited in the
33 county general fund.
34 Section 3. This act shall become effective on September
35 1, 2026.
